-- China CSRC to Limit Use of Stock Sale Proceeds, Securities Journal Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-21T23:45:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/china-csrc-to-limit-use-of-stock-sale-proceeds-securities-journal-reports.html
The China Securities Regulatory
Commission will “in principle” limit publicly traded companies
from using share-sale proceeds to repay bank loans or replenish
working capital, the China Securities Journal reported today,
citing an unidentified person.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  